window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He never wanted to become a beast. But the only way to stay a man requires the taming touch of a woman.</p> <p>Marcus escaped the doctors who thought it was okay to experiment on him. Totally expected to savor freedom far, far away from the evil wrought by the Chimaeram Clinic.</p> <p>Instead, he finds himself inexplicably drawn back to the place that made him a monster.</p> <p>And what do monsters do best but terrorize humans?</p> <p>When he kidnaps Jayda, he has no thought other than to make a certain doctor pay. However, taking an alluring woman to his lair means having her close. Hearing her. Smelling her....</p> <p>Remembering what it means to be a man.</p> <p>Wanting to be her lover.</p> <p>Is she his salvation, or his downfall? Because there is only one punishment for a project gone rogue....</p>"; 
